Background

		Mr. Viktoras R. Sekmakas, also known as Viktor, has been the Executive Vice President of PPG Industries Inc. since September 1, 2012. Mr. Sekmakas has also been the President of Europe at PPG Industries since September 1, 2011. He served as Senior Vice President of Industrial Coatings at PPG Industries since August 1, 2010. He served as the President of Asia & Pacific of PPG Industries from July 1, 2008 to September 1, 2011 and also served as its Vice President of Coatings ... since July 1, 2006. Mr. Sekmakas served as Managing Director of Asia/Pacific Operation of PPG Industries since July 1, 2006. He served with PPG in 1997 as Market Development Manager for powder coatings and moved to the Asia/Pacific region in 2001 and served as Managing Director of Coatings and General Manager of Industrial Coatings, Asia in March 2005. Mr. Sekmakas worked for Valspar as new business manager, starting in 1990 and for Lilly Industries starting in 1995 as electrocoat market manager. He earned a bachelor's degree in chemical engineering from the University of Illinois.Read Full Background




